      "notes": "Alpaca Options launched commission-free in 2023. Native multi-leg spread orders supported via the 'complex order' API. Reg T margin only \u2014 no portfolio margin, so 3\u00d7 leverage on defined-risk spreads is not feasible (would cap at ~2\u00d7 gross). Routing is PFOF which trades execution quality for $0 commissions. Fill quality has been documented as worse on 2+ leg orders."
